elements.name: Debería permitir al usuario editar una página existente

steps.name: I open the Ghost login page
I navigate to the pages page
I enter to create a new page
I enter page details "My New Page 1" "This is the content of my first page"
I navigate to the pages page
I open the page with title "My New Page 1"
I edit the page title to "Updated Page Title" and content "Updated content of the page"
I navigate to the pages page
I should see the page "Updated Page Title" in the pages list
